dialogue.introduction: Light cruiser, Tama. I'm not a cat, meow.
dialogue.library_intro: Second of the Kuma-class light cruisers, Tama nya. I did my duty as a torpedo squadron flagship, Nya! Nya? Tama's my name, but I'm not a cat!
dialogue.secretary2: Ha! Without thinking, my hand... stop teasing me~!
dialogue.secretarymarried: Thanks for the hard work, meow. Take a break with Tama, meow. Meoooow~
dialogue.wedding: Admiral, please stop calling me with chan at the end, it sort of... feels different.
dialogue.show_players_score: Letter addressed to the Admiral, nya.
dialogue.equipment1: This is fine, nya. Meow problem.
dialogue.supply: This is fine, nya. Meow problem.
dialogue.docking_moderate_damage: In the dock, Tama will curl up, meow.
dialogue.ship_construction: A new ship has finished constructing, meow.
dialogue.return_from_sortie: Look's like the fleets returned, nya.
dialogue.start_a_sortie: You want to borrow Tama's hand? It can't be helped, meow.
dialogue.mvp: Tama's excellence? Nya~, that's just my high hunter's instincts... nya.
dialogue.rainy_season_2015: On a rainy day, I wanna curl up in the room meow. I'm sleepy meow. Good night meow.
dialogue.midsummer_2015: It's summer nya. It's a little hot nya. It's so hot it makes me wanna roll over onto my back and sleep nya. Nyaa~
dialogue.end_of_year_2015: It's almost mew year. A season where everyone gets their paws busy. I shall purrseed to the corner and sleep. Meow...
dialogue.new_year_2016: Happy Nya Year. Please treat meow well this year as well. ...nyaa~
